{"title":"ใช้งาน OpenVSCode Server จาก Gitpod กัน","link":"https://www.somkiat.cc/openvscode-server-from-gitpod/","date":1633018556000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div id=\"page\"><article><div id=\"content_box\"><header><div><p><time>September 30, 2021</time> <span><a href=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/category/programming/\" rel=\"category tag\">Programming</a>, <a href=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/category/tools/\" rel=\"category tag\">Tools</a></span></p></div></header><div><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/gitpod-open-vscode.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/gitpod-open-vscode.jpeg 900w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/gitpod-open-vscode-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/gitpod-open-vscode-768x432.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\"></figure><p>ทาง <a href=\"https://www.gitpod.io/blog/openvscode-server-launch\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gitpod</a> ได้เปิด open source project ชื่อว่า <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/gitpod-io/openvscode-server/\" target=\"_blank\">OpenVSCode Server</a></strong> มาให้ใช้งานกัน<br>ซึ่งก็คือ VSCode remote ให้ใช้งานผ่าน web browser ได้เลย<br>หรือมันก็คือ GitHub Codespace แบบ open source นั่นเอง</p><p><strong>โดยที่ project นี้ได้รับการสนับสนุนจาก</strong></p><ul><li>GitLab</li><li>VMware</li><li>Uber</li><li>SAP</li><li>Sourcegraph</li><li>RStudio</li><li>SUSE</li><li>และอื่น ๆ อีกมากมาย</li></ul><p>การใช้งานสามารถใช้ได้ทั้งแบบปกติ หรือ Docker ก็ได้อีกด้วย<br>ลองไปใช้งานกันดูครับ</p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/7202b8da-gitpod-screenshot-1024x675-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/7202b8da-gitpod-screenshot-1024x675-1.png 1024w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/7202b8da-gitpod-screenshot-1024x675-1-300x198.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/7202b8da-gitpod-screenshot-1024x675-1-768x506.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure></div><div><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e5cb9aad7bf4f0e43462bd51d6ff7021?s=90&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\" srcset=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e5cb9aad7bf4f0e43462bd51d6ff7021?s=180&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\" height=\"90\" width=\"90\"></p><h4>Article by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/somkiatspns\">Somkiat Puisungnoen</a></h4><p>To be Craftmanship</p></div></div></article></div></div>","author":"somkiat","siteTitle":"cc :: somkiat","siteHash":"3a23a5a4389e1e40c6fbb16520a8cc20df5b3591c25145ce72aaa18b19e48201","entryHash":"734d846d76bda081fa37185599559b18e17d869b23bab3ee37d9bc4267a28f3d","category":"Thai"}